      "text": " Response Time:\n• Target: < 2 seconds (P95)\n• Voice: < 3 seconds total\n\n AI Models:\n• LLM: LLaMA (open source)\n• STT: Whisper\n• TTS: Coqui TTS\n• Translation: MarianMT\n\n Data Storage:\n• Redis: Session/cache\n• PostgreSQL: Structured data\n• Vector DB: Embeddings\n• MongoDB: Logs/documents\n\n Languages:\n• English, Spanish\n• Hindi, Telugu\n\n Security:\n• JWT authentication\n• AES-256 encryption\n• Rate limiting\n• GDPR compliant",
