      "fontSize": 17.125580070554754,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "User (Voice in Hindi):\n\"मुझे शादी के लिए एक लाल रंग\nकी साड़ी चाहिए\"\n\n↓ System Processing ↓\n\n1. STT: Convert to text\n2. Translation: Hindi → English\n3. NLU: Intent = design_request\n   Entities: occasion=wedding,\n             color=red, type=saree\n4. Design Agent: Start workflow\n5. SQL Agent: Query products\n6. Response: \"I found 3 red\n   wedding sarees...\"\n7. Translation: English → Hindi\n8. TTS: Convert to speech\n\n↓ User receives ↓\n\nVoice (Hindi): \"मैंने 3 लाल शादी\nकी साड़ियाँ पाईं...\" + Rich Cards",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "User (Voice in Hindi):\n\"मुझे शादी के लिए एक लाल रंग\nकी साड़ी चाहिए\"\n\n↓ System Processing ↓\n\n1. STT: Convert to text\n2. Translation: Hindi → English\n3. NLU: Intent = design_request\n   Entities: occasion=wedding,\n             color=red, type=saree\n4. Design Agent: Start workflow\n5. SQL Agent: Query products\n6. Response: \"I found 3 red\n   wedding sarees...\"\n7. Translation: English → Hindi\n8. TTS: Convert to speech\n\n↓ User receives ↓\n\nVoice (Hindi): \"मैंने 3 लाल शादी\nकी साड़ियाँ पाईं...\" + Rich Cards",
